[{"Id": 1014993, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Quoted from Uddat Daee, Imam Ali Amir Momeneen (a) is reported to have said: When you intend to go to sleep, you may put your right hand under your right cheek and say this devotional statement. If you say it before going to sleep, Almighty Allah will guard you against raiding thieves and against demolition, and the angels will implore Almighty Allah to forgive you…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Kitaab Uddat Daee mein Hazrat Ameerul Momeneen (a) se riwaayat hai keh jab tum mein se koi shakhs soney ka iraada kare to apna daaya’n haath (right hand) daayne rukhsaar (right cheek) ke neeche rakhe aur yeh kahe. Pas jo shakhs sotey waqt yeh dua padhe to Allah taala usey chor daaku aur chhat-taley dabne se mehfooz rakhega aur farishte uske liye maghferat talab karenge…", "UrduDescription": "کتاب عدۃ الداعی میں ہے کہ امیر المؤمنینؑ سے روایت ہے : جب تم میں سے کوئی شخص سونے کا ارادہ کرے تو اپنادایاں ہاتھ دائیں رخسار کے نیچے رکھ کر یہ کہے۔ لہٰذا جو شخص سوتے وقت اس دعا کو پڑھے اﷲتعالیٰ اسے چور ڈاکو اور چھت تلے دبنے سے محفوظ رکھے گااور فرشتے اس کے لئے مغفرت طلب کریں گے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueS